            <div class="mt-5 p-3 rounded bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10">
              <p class="text-xs text-primary leading-relaxed"><span class="font-bold">Offline verification:</span> Ramp inspectors cache ~193 NAA public keys on their device. When a pilot presents a credential via QR or NFC, the inspector verifies the issuer's signature locally - no internet required. Proven by SITA in a 2020 proof of concept with the CAAC.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

